short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Default branching based on the title of stories in Jira and integration with Microsoft Azure DevOps Repos

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Generates a branch name based on the current JIRA issue view.

Integration for create branches with Microsoft Azure DevOps Repos. Branch name automatically contains Jira issue key (necessary for linking to Jira) and the issue summary.

You can get the branch name and git commands to build it.

Open source version (Without integration git): https://github.com/alissonsolitto/generator-branch
